# Lessons

A structured set of lessons for working biomedical scientists. You can
follow the lessons in order or drop in wherever you need to. Each topic
ships three things: a **Typer CLI**, **R + Python primary notebooks**, and
**R + Python eye-candy notebooks** — so the lesson lives where the
deliverables live.

## The spine

```{toctree}
:maxdepth: 1

introduction
elements-of-style-rules
command-line-and-git-bash
version-control
conda-environments
interactive-computing
reusable-clis
containers
nextflow
